---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Systems architect and AI developer based in Safford, Arizona. Building automation and AI agents for businesses."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <h1
            class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50 mb-8"
          >
            About
          </h1>

          <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p>
              I'm a systems architect and AI developer based in <strong
                >Safford, Arizona</strong
              >. I build automation systems and AI agents that reduce manual
              work and keep teams consistent.
            </p>

            <p>
              My background is in building complex software systems—multi-agent
              AI frameworks, workflow engines, and developer tools. I've spent
              years figuring out how to make AI actually useful in production,
              not just impressive in demos.
            </p>

            <p>
              What I've learned: the difference between "working" and "reliable"
              is everything. A workflow that runs 95% of the time is a
              liability. A workflow that handles edge cases, logs what happened,
              and alerts you when something's off—that's infrastructure you can
              build on.
            </p>

            <h2 class="font-display">How I work</h2>

            <p>
              I bias toward action. Instead of spending weeks on specifications,
              I'd rather build a working prototype in days and iterate from
              there. You learn more from a running system than from any
              document.
            </p>

            <p>
              Everything I build comes with documentation. Not because it's
              required, but because systems without documentation become
              problems. When I hand off a project, you should understand exactly
              what it does and how to troubleshoot it.
            </p>

            <h2 class="font-display">Why Safford?</h2>

            <p>
              I work with businesses locally in Graham County and Eastern
              Arizona, as well as remotely with teams across the country. Being
              in a small town means I understand the constraints small
              businesses actually face—tight budgets, small teams, no dedicated
              IT staff. I build for that reality.
            </p>

            <h2 class="font-display">Open source</h2>

            <p>
              I maintain several open-source projects, including frameworks for
              multi-agent AI coordination and developer tools for building
              reliable AI systems. You can see my work on <a
                href="https://github.com/Mnehmos"
                class="text-copper hover:underline">GitHub</a
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50 mb-4">
              Location
            </h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300">
              Safford, Arizona<br />
              Graham County<br />
              Eastern Arizona
            </p>
            <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 text-sm mt-4">
              Serving local businesses + remote teams
            </p>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50 mb-4">
              Specialties
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 text-copper"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Workflow automation
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 text-copper"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                AI agents & LLM systems
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 text-copper"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                API integrations
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 text-copper"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Multi-agent frameworks
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-4 h-4 text-copper"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                >
                  <path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Internal tools & dashboards
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="bg-white dark:bg-stone-800 rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 p-6"
          >
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50 mb-4">
              Values
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 text-sm">
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50"
                  >Ship fast</span
                >
                <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mt-1">
                  Working prototypes over endless planning
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50"
                  >Document hard</span
                >
                <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mt-1">
                  If it's not documented, it doesn't exist
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="font-medium text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-50"
                  >Build reliable</span
                >
                <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mt-1">
                  Systems that work at 3am without you
                </p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <a
            href={`${base}contact`}
            class="block bg-stone-900 text-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 hover:bg-stone-800 transition-colors"
          >
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Work with me</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm mb-4">
              Let's talk about what you want to automate.
            </p>
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center text-copper text-sm font-medium"
            >
              Book a call
              <svg
                class="w-4 h-4 ml-1"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    font-family: "Space Grotesk", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  :global(.dark) .prose h2 {
    color: #fafaf9;
  }

  :global(:not(.dark)) .prose h2 {
    color: #1c1917;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .prose strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  :global(.dark) .prose strong {
    color: #fafaf9;
  }

  :global(:not(.dark)) .prose strong {
    color: #1c1917;
  }
</style>
